# Normalize line endings. The repo stores LF and every checkout — Windows
# included — gets LF, so `core.autocrlf=true` no longer yields a CRLF working
# tree that makes Prettier's `endOfLine: lf` check fail locally while passing
# in CI. `text=auto` lets git auto-detect and skip binary files.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Be explicit about the binary assets so they're never EOL-converted.
*.png binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.icns binary
